                        <support>1 papyrus ; 14.8 x 25.8 cm.</support>
                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">A medium-brown and comparatively thick papyrus in good condition; almost regularly cut at the top, right and bottom. There is one Kollesis about 5.5 cm from the left edge. A vertical strip at the upper part to the left has been lost as a result of a fold. Although the papyrus is damaged at the middle and at the kollesis, most of the text is preserved.</ab>
                        </condition>
